
Compile Command Linux
g++ -o test test.cpp -lglut -lGLU -lGL

Compile Command Windows
g++ -c -o test.o test.cpp -I"C:\MinGW\include"
g++ -o test.exe test.o -L"C:\MinGW\lib" -lglu32 -lglut32 -lfreeglut -lopengl32 -Wl,--subsystem,windows


Sudo needed

sudo apt-get install mesa-common-dev
sudo apt-get install freeglut3-dev
sudo apt-get install libglew-dev